ndependence ", "last_comment_created": 1783847665552, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 79, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 2731, "heightRatio": 149, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HM9GX4EbEAAmeXN.jpg", "height": 4096}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 104, "created": 1783781342000, "id": "2075955528401104933", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2070478338922258433/UUPG17op_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Tony Seruga", "username": "TonySeruga"}, "content": "\ud83d\udea8 More Americans Died on One British Prison Ship Than in Every Battle of the Revolution Combined. The Empire Called It \u201cPolicy.\u201d \u2620\ufe0f\n\nThey don\u2019t teach this.\n\n11,500+ American prisoners died on British prison ships during the Revolutionary War.\n\n6,800 died in combat.\n\nLet that", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 3818}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqe5vTo", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "apu", "id": 8724664, "raw_content": "I wasn\u2019t a huge Graham fan, but my God, compared to you faggots he was like a saint.\n\nA Trump ally. Someone who actually spent his life progressing Republican issues and opposing the left. Not by screeching from his mom\u2019s basement but by fighting in Washington DC.\n\n> he was muh WAR MONGRUR!!! Muh WAR MOHGREURRRERR. Burn in hell WAR MONGGRUHHHH\n\nholy shit you people are fucking retarded. It is so painfully obvious you have no understanding of any war, or why Graham supported them or not.\n\nYour entire philosophy is just to be an ignorant faggot who opposes all wars out of principle. You have the foreign policy chops of a child.\n\nHe would annihilate any of you retards in a debate on any war you are so upset about, regardless of if the war was justified or not. He\u2019s 10x better educated than any of you illiterate pieces of trash. He actually dedicated time, money and effort to becoming intelligent. You are just faggots with big egos who never admit when you\u2019re wrong, like little children.\n\nCharlie Kirk said that you learn a lot about people based on how they react to death. This is a great example of that. Graham was not the best senator but he was a reasonably decent Republican senator and he helped MAGA quite a bit, campaigning for Trump and voting with him. \n\nThere is no good reason to be celebrating his death, but you fags are basically the same as people who celebrated Kirk\u2019s death: arrogant pompous clowns cheering for death because you saw a few TikTok videos and have determined the decedent is EVIL WAR MONGRUH / EVIL RACIST.\n\nI assure you, all of you have a far better chance of going to hell than Graham. Everyone who supported the Iraq War is not some evil Hitleresque supervillain. People can reasonably disagree on when and how we use our military. Supporting the war in Ukraine doesn\u2019t mean you deserve to die. You unhinged psychos may want to take some time and reflect on how you\u2019re the mirror image of a leftist demon before it\u2019s too late.", "author": "STFUmuslimCUCKS", "created": 1783840823063, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "weltallic", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Reaction to Graham\u2019s death shows the user base here is just as low IQ and demonic as Reddit.", "last_comment_created": 1783848535248, "content": "<p>I wasn\u2019t a huge Graham fan, but my God, compared to you faggots he was like a saint.</p>\n<p>A Trump ally. Someone who actually spent his life progressing Republican issues and opposing the left. Not by screeching from his mom\u2019s basement but by fighting in Washington DC.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>he was muh WAR MONGRUR!!! Muh WAR MOHGREURRRERR. Burn in hell WAR MONGGRUHHHH</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>holy shit you people are fucking retarded. It is so painfully obvious you have no understanding of any war, or why Graham supported them or not.</p>\n<p>Your entire philosophy is just to be an ignorant faggot who opposes all wars out of principle. You have the foreign policy chops of a child.</p>\n<p>He would annihilate any of you retards in a debate on any war you are so upset about, regardless of if the war was justified or not. He\u2019s 10x better educated than any of you illiterate pieces of trash. He actually dedicated time, money and effort to becoming intelligent. You are just faggots with big egos who never admit when you\u2019re wrong, like little children.</p>\n<p>Charlie Kirk said that you learn a lot about people based on how they react to death. This is a great example of that. Graham was not the best senator but he was a reasonably decent Republican senator and he helped MAGA quite a bit, campaigning for Trump and voting with him.</p>\n<p>There is no good reason to be celebrating his death, but you fags are basically the same as people who celebrated Kirk\u2019s death: arrogant pompous clowns cheering for death because you saw a few TikTok videos and have determined the decedent is EVIL WAR MONGRUH / EVIL RACIST.</p>\n<p>I assure you, all of you have a far better chance of going to hell than Graham. Everyone who supported the Iraq War is not some evil Hitleresque supervillain. People can reasonably disagree on when and how we use our military. Supporting the war in Ukraine doesn\u2019t mean you deserve to die. You unhinged psychos may want to take some time and reflect on how you\u2019re the mirror image of a leftist demon before it\u2019s too late.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 29, "score_up": 26, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "BE\u00a0\u00a0LESS\u00a0\u00a0RETARDED", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2075869804670456199", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqe4pDd", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 87, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8724259, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1783817138873, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Dicyanin2C", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBqe4pDd.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/lozzafox/status/2075869804670456199", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "London Promotional Video Doesn\u2019t Have Any White People", "last_comment_created": 1783821303628, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 87, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1783756183000, "id": "2075850006502756460", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HMkSaz5XMAAC62Q.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/20742092718